  m_Name: Trial of Culling
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuestDefinition
  QuestId: Trial of Culling
  QuestTitle: Trial of Culling
  QuestObjective: Kill 5 Minions
  QuestDescription: 'A soft voice echoes in your mind, gentle as drifting ash. "The
    fields have grown unruly. A handful of lesser creatures wander too far from their
    place. Remove five of them, and restore a sense of balance."


    There is no
    urgency in the request. No anger. No fear. Only quiet observation.'
  QuestOutcome: You sense no gratitude will follow your task, only silence... and
    the faint impression that something unseen is taking careful note of how efficiently
    you end a life.
  MaxProgres: 5
